            "author_association": "NONE",
            "body": "This is what I came up with, if anyone else is interested:\n```\nvim.lsp.config('*', {\n\tcapabilities = {\n\t\ttextDocument = {\n\t\t\tcompletion = {\n\t\t\t\tcompletionItem = {\n\t\t\t\t\tsnippetSupport = false\n\t\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t}\n\t}\n})\n```",
